  <thing id="spMPRelTxt" name="Relay Text" description="You cause a text message of up to 25 words to appear on the screen of an electronic device capable of receiving such messages, such as a cell phone, smart phone, or computer. If the device is turned on, the message appears instantly; if not, the message appears as soon as someone turns it on. \n\nThe message remains onscreen until read, then disappears, leaving no electronic record of its appearance. You must have seen the device to send a message to it." compset="Spell" summary="You can transmit a message of up to 25 words via electronic device to someone you know.">
