  <thing id="ipMPBladeg" name="Bladegun" description="A bladegun is a magic firearm that transforms into a magic short sword (and back again) upon command. \nThe firearm and short sword versions of the weapon possess the same enhancement bonus (+1 to +5). Turning the firearm into a short sword—and vice versa— takes a move action. A bladegun in firearm form must be loaded with ammunition to fire (as any gun)." compset="ItemPower" summary="Firearm that transforms into a magic short sword (and back again) upon command">
