  <thing id="ipMPPsycho" name="Psycho" description="This battered weapon constantly drips a small amount of blood. The weapon doubles critical threat range.\n\n Any creature who handles a psycho weapon suffers Madness. As found in the Pathfinder Role Playing Game - Game Mastery Guide \n\nThis type of Insanity remains as long as the weapon is in hand, and disappears when it is no longer wielded. \n\nThe Insanity cannot be overcome in any way while the weapon is wielded." compset="ItemPower" summary="Doubles critical threat range." uniqueness="unique">
