  <thing id="cMPTurnHum" name="Turn Humans" description="Calling upon higher powers, you cause Humans to flee from the might of your unleashed divine energy.\n\n{b}Benefit{/b}: You can, as a standard action, use one of your uses of channel positive energy to cause all Humans within 30 feet of you to flee, as if panicked. Humans receive a Will save to negate the effect. The DC for this Will save is equal to 10 + 1/2 your level + your Charisma modifier. Humans that fail their save flee for 1 minute. Intelligent Humans receive a new saving throw each round to end the effect. If you use channel energy in this way, it has no other effect (it does not heal or harm nearby creatures)." compset="CustomSpec" summary="Your Channel Energy can make Humans flee." uniqueness="unique">
