  <thing id="cMPEmpSpl" name="Empower Spell" description="You can increase the power of your spells, causing them to deal more damage.\n\n{b}Benefit{/b}: All variable, numeric effects of an empowered spell are increased by half.\n\nSaving throws and opposed rolls are not affected, nor are spells without random variables. An empowered spell uses up a spell slot two levels higher than the spell&apos;s actual level." compset="CustomSpec" summary="Numeric effects of a spell are increased 50%. +2 Levels." uniqueness="unique">
