  <thing id="irMPSurDet" name="Ring of Surveillance Detection" description="This ring pulses dimly when electronic devices are monitoring the wearer. The ring can detect a working video camera, microphone, motion detector, or other sensor within 50 feet. By taking a full-round action, the wearer can locate the direction and distance to the device. \n\nIt grants a +5 circumstance bonus on Perception checks." compset="Ring">
