  <thing id="ioMPUnivID" name="Universal ID" description="This blank piece of plastic is the size of a credit card and can transform into any form of ID on command, including photo, holographic imprints, and watermarks (as per the magic ID spell). It does not create a magnetic strip or other form of nonvisual information. The card must be held by the user for the image to be changed." compset="Wondrous">
