    </thing>
  <thing id="ioMPSynWth" name="Synchronicity Watch" description="Department-7 may not be the richest organization in the world, nor is it the best networked, but it does provide agents with some of the most unique equipment in the field. Members of Department-7 may buy this item for the cost of 1 Prestige Point.\n\nA wrist or pocket watch that allows agents to move through crowds more easily than usual. Once per day, the watch can be used to activate a limited version of the synchronicity spell. It works exactly the same way as the spell except that the duration is only 10 rounds." compset="Wondrous">
