  <thing id="fMPAAstrol" name="Astrology" description="{b}Benefit{/b}: You gain a +2 bonus to Knowledge (planes) and Spellcraft.\n\nIf you have 10 or more ranks in one of these skills, the bonus increases to +4 for that skill\n\n{b}Special{/b}: You can use Knowledge (planes), instead of his Knowledge (arcana) skill." compset="Feat" summary="The study of supernatural effects of celestial bodies." uniqueness="useronce">
