  <thing id="fMPACermCs" name="Ceremonial Caster" description="{b}Benefit{/b}: When you cast an Abjuration spell against a target with spell resistance, it treats the spell resistance of the target as 2 lower than its actual SR.\n\nYou get a +2 bonus on concentration checks made to cast an Abjuration spell.\n\n{b}Level Increase{/b}: None" compset="Feat" summary="The supernatural study of the Abjuration school of magic." uniqueness="useronce">
