  <thing id="fMPACorres" name="Correspondencism" description="{b}Benefit{/b}: You choose a knowledge skill. For every 5 ranks in that chosen skill, it provides the Spellcraft skill a +2 Insight bonus." compset="Feat" summary="The study of supernatural effects of various philosophies and how they relate to each other." uniqueness="useronce">
