  <thing id="ioMPACsRdG" name="Crossroad&apos;s Guitar" description="Legend says that in the dark of night, meeting at a crossroad, you can find fortune and fame, but at a price.\n\nThis electric guitar grants the holder a +10 to Perform (String Instruments) skill and grants the owner the choice of one Performer&apos;s Training Technique.\n\nThis does come with a cost though. Once the owner reaches the age of 27, (if older, after one year from possessing the item), he will have to make a Will save every month of 15 +1 per month for the next year or die. If the owner survives he will be infected with madness as found in the Pathfinder Role Playing Game - Game Mastery Guide.\n\nThe Crossroad Item Power can be applied to any item used with the perform skill. Its cost is $200,000 per item." compset="Wondrous">
