~ bonus on Spellcraft checks
#applybonus[Bonus,hero.child[skSpellcr],field[actUser].value*2]
endif]]></eval>
    </thing>
  <thing id="cMPATkVill" name="It takes a Village" description="A Ritual spell is always greatly enhanced when there are multiple Crafters working together. When a Crafter with this Training is leading a Ritual Spellcrafting, for every 3 Crafters that assist, assume that a fourth assistant is helping as well. The Crafter will receive the full benefit of 4 assistants. This ability requires no Hero Points, and is always active." compset="CustomSpec" uniqueness="unique">
