  <thing id="cMPALngDsC" name="Long Distance Call" description="Should a Spirit-Crafter cast a Communion Spell; he may contact a ghost from the Spirit Realm. The Crafter may ask one additional question of this ghost, beyond the number allowed normally by the spell. If the Crafter knows the name of a specific ghost, he may request information from that individual. This ability requires 1 Hero Point in addition to the requirements of crafting the spell." compset="CustomSpec" uniqueness="unique">
