  <thing id="trMPAMHer" name="Magical Heritage" description="You have magical ability in your background, such as a sorcerer in your bloodline, or you gained access to magic at a particularly young age (by discovering a spellbook in your attic, for example). As a result, you mastered some basic spellcasting.\n \nBenefit: Choose  a 0-level arcane spell. You may cast this spell once per day." compset="Trait" uniqueness="useronce">
