  <thing id="cMPASSummo" name="Summon" description="School: Conjuration\nCasting Time: 1 Standard Action\nComponents: as per Archetype\nRange: Close (25&apos; + 5&apos; per Caster Level)\nTargets/Effects/Area: One Summoned Creature or Prepared Object\nDuration: See Text\nSaving Throw: None\nSpell Resistance: No\n\nIf this Conjuration spell is successfully crafted, it will send a mystic summons to an extra-planar creature, pulling it from where it originates, and instantly transporting it to where the Crafter awaits. This spell may also summon a prepared object or piece of equipment from any location to where the Crafter awaits. And lastly, a Summoning spell may also be used to hide a container within the Ethereal Plane for a certain period of time." compset="CustomSpec" summary="Summons to an extra-planar creature" uniqueness="unique">
