  <thing id="cMPANecrom" name="School of Necromancy" description="This School of Magic deals with the darker desires within us all, and generally with issues that are considered &quot;evil&quot; in nature. \n\nNecromancy spells manipulate the power of death, unlife, and the life force. \n\nSpells involving undead creatures make up a large part of this school, as are spells that deal with fear and curses. These are the hallmarks of Necromancy.\n\nThe School of Necromancy includes the following spells; Curse, Death, Fear, Harm, &amp; Spirit" compset="CustomSpec" uniqueness="unique">
